sentences: David Montgomery (born 8 February 1937 in Brooklyn, New York) is a photographer known for his portraits of the rich and famous.
He also photographed Queen Elizabeth II in 1967, being the first American to do so, after which he said that he was never frightened of a subject again, going on to photograph five Prime Ministers.
